  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "English.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, I forget.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll switch it for one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The most important, what the market had, that it provided relationships, which we and people, like the people, peasants, which otherwise wouldn't have too much occasion to meet Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it provided business.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, now when there's no Jewish people here, there's no more market here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's, it's become a park now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it's-- everything is gone now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came of a unique family, because my grandmother was a daughter of a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the mother and the father was extremely orthodox.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Therefore, my grandmother would wear the traditional orthodox gown.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was wearing a wig, but not to beautify herself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the woman at that time, as I remember them, the religious, Jewish women, will wear either a wig or a kerchief, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she would wear very conservative clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was very modest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And most of all, she lived with the Jewish laws, customs, and tradition.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We strictly observe the Jewish holidays, the Sabbath, and all those things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, as I-- previous testimony, she would not permit me to take a piece of-- a bite of food without saying a, saying a prayer.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the stories which I told previously I'm not going to repeat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At the other hand, my parents was religious.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By today's standards, they would-- could almost call them orthodox.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then they didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't  wear the traditional garb.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "However, they observed the Jewish laws and traditions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My-- we get a, a Jewish education, you know, and this education in the Pole-- in the school, which I attended.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we observed the holidays.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And speaking about clothes, I'll tell you a very little story.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When we lived in Poland, regardless how rich or poor we were, the Jewish people, twice a year, and regardless how much clothes you had, the Jewish people, for Pass-- for Passover, for the high holidays-- Rosh Hashanah, Yom Kuppur-- the children would always get new clothes.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at that time, we didn't have big department stores or markets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So therefore, we used to go to the dressmaker to get made new dresses, to the shoemaker to get new shoes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I used to get patent leather shoes with white socks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was-- and one time, I got a dress, a two-piece dress, with a sailor color, you know, from navy blue gabardine with white stripes on the collar and a pleated skirt.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when my mother went with me to the dressmaker to pick it up, I I was felt-- came home and tried it on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I felt like the whole world belongs to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I had such a beautiful new dress.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And as a child, I wanted to go out and show all my friends.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my mother said, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Itka, ?] I would advise you not to put on the dress now, because it's for the holidays.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In case something happens, you will not have it for the holidays.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I insisted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So my mother said, I guess you're only going to learn from your experiences.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And but it's your responsibility.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I promised.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I said, mommy, I will not-- I will take good care.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I was a tomboy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we had in Ciechanow, a river.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It's called [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Ladinya ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And at the banks of the river, there was, you know grass, a lot of trees.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the kids said, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Itka, ?] let's look down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we'll play there a little.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then they challenged.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Let's see who could climb up fastest on the tree.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I was a tomboy and fast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So I started to climbing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I was beating somebody else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I don't know whether they want to scare me or what was the reason.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They said, Itka, your mother is coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I got so frightened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I remembered I wasn't supposed to do that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So I wanted to get off fast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I ripped my skirt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Cannot imagine how I felt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Regretful, felt guilty for not listening to my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I-- it was pleated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "So I took-- put over the pleat like this with tears in my eyes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I came home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "My mother looked at me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "She didn't have to ask anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "She said, take off the dress.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And I'll fix it for you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And regardless, whether you going to-- you can have a choice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Wear your old dress or the new when it's fixed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "But you're going to go to synagogue for the holiday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And she said, remember Itka, there is a lesson here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "You never take chances on something you cannot afford to lose.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
